</h3><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-53_">Vital signs
</h3><p class="sc-hOGkXu hVdrsp pf-55_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Vital signs are the primary indicators of physiological status, including temperature, pulse, blood pressure, respiratory rate, and oxygen saturation.
